      "writtenOn": "2021-04-16T17:38:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Hmm, in this case we can\u0027t get Attempt proto from CQDaemon -- but ideally we\u0027d still like to record such aborted runs in the BQ table...\n\nSounds like we\u0027d either have to construct an Attempt proto here, or just not record such runs before fully migrating?",
